title: Is Starbucks’ Pumpkin Spice Latte Full of Toxins?
subtitle: Among the claims made in a viral graphic are that Starbucks Pumpkin Spice Lattes do not contain any pumpkin, that the flavoring contains high fructose corn syrup, and that a specific ingredient is dangerous.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Starbucks' Pumpkin Spice Latte contains numerous toxins, and the coffee giant is hiding the drink's ingredient list.
